=\"AppDay_FFOs_Ibague_Showcase\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0964-252x189.jpg\" width=\"252\" height=\"189\" /></a> Una app de contactos muy muy chachi[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_176\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"252\"]<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/image3026.png\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-176\" alt=\"Unas de las apps que se mostraron en mi celular\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/image3026-252x183.png\" width=\"252\" height=\"183\" /></a> Unas de las apps que se mostraron en mi celular[/caption]\r\n\r\nY pues como se debe terminar todo buen evento, con una <del datetime=\"2013-08-31T22:04:56+00:00\">explosión</del>, con REGALOS!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0976.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-190\" alt=\"AppDay_FFOs_Ibague_Gifs\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0976-252x189.jpg\" width=\"252\" height=\"189\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0975.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-189\" alt=\"AppDay_FFOs_Ibague_Gifs\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0975-252x189.jpg\" width=\"252\" height=\"189\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0974.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-188\" alt=\"AppDay_FFOs_Ibague_Gifs\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0974-252x189.jpg\" width=\"252\" height=\"189\" /></a> <a href=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0973.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-187\" alt=\"AppDay_FFOs_Ibague_Gifs\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/IMG_0973-252x189.jpg\" width=\"252\" height=\"189\" /></a>','FirefoxOS AppsDay Ibagué ','','inherit','open','open','','166-revision-v1','','','2013-08-31 17:37:59','2013-